{
  "id": "5b2650e84f75b00014431e6b",
  "title": "新しいS字曲線に投資した方が得",
  "created": 1529237739,
  "updated": 1566377597,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5b2650e84f75b00014431e6b",
      "text": "新しいS字曲線に投資した方が得",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529237739,
      "updated": 1529237759
    },
    {
      "id": "5b2650feaff09e0000a7c912",
      "text": "\t投資とリターンの関係が[S字曲線]になるような対象について",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529237759,
      "updated": 1529238246
    },
    {
      "id": "5b265145aff09e0000a7c915",
      "text": " 序盤はそれに投資することが損に見える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529237829,
      "updated": 1529238036
    },
    {
      "id": "5b265177aff09e0000a7c916",
      "text": " \tしかし、投資を続けると投資対効果が上がっていくので、投資が得になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529237880,
      "updated": 1529238039
    },
    {
      "id": "5b2651e8aff09e0000a7c91b",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/c0594d915a6a9b7193de10a6b7d16b9e]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529237992,
      "updated": 1529238004
    },
    {
      "id": "5b265196aff09e0000a7c917",
      "text": "\t問題はこの後",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529237911,
      "updated": 1529237915
    },
    {
      "id": "5b26519baff09e0000a7c91a",
      "text": " 緩やかに投資対効果が減少していくと、そのうちまた投資が損になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529237915,
      "updated": 1529238052
    },
    {
      "id": "5b265225aff09e0000a7c91c",
      "text": " しかしその時点で他のまだ投資していないS字曲線と比較すると、まだこの曲線に投資することの方が得に見える。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529238053,
      "updated": 1529238103
    },
    {
      "id": "5b265257aff09e0000a7c91d",
      "text": " こうして古いS字曲線に投資し続けてしまう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529238103,
      "updated": 1566377593
    },
    {
      "id": "5d5d0678aff09e00001b98db",
      "text": " しかし長期的視野では実は新しいS字曲線に投資した方が得である",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1566377593,
      "updated": 1566377597
    },
    {
      "id": "5b2651d2aff09e000064ca07",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/e841e6fa18dd6abda2a62de8516545a8]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529237972,
      "updated": 1529237972
    },
    {
      "id": "5b265196aff09e0000a7c918",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529237911,
      "updated": 1529237911
    },
    {
      "id": "5b2650feaff09e0000a7c913",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529237759,
      "updated": 1529237759
    },
    {
      "id": "5b2650feaff09e0000a7c911",
      "text": " 4年前の[新しい曲線に投資した方が得]の精製版",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529237759,
      "updated": 1529237779
    },
    {
      "id": "5b2650ffaff09e0000a7c914",
      "text": "\t知識への投資がS字曲線に従うのかどうかに関してはまだ確信がない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529237760,
      "updated": 1529239154
    },
    {
      "id": "5b265c40aff09e000069a485",
      "text": " \t[nishio.icon]は昔は素朴に「指数関数的だ」と思っていたが、S字曲線だと考える方が色々なものとの整合性が良い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529240640,
      "updated": 1529240819
    },
    {
      "id": "5b265672aff09e0000a7c91f",
      "text": " \t[学習曲線がS字曲線になる原理]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529239154,
      "updated": 1529239543
    },
    {
      "id": "5b265656aff09e0000a7c91e",
      "text": "  [勝者総取り環境下で知識の効用がS字]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529239127,
      "updated": 1529240591
    },
    {
      "id": "5b265c0faff09e000069a484",
      "text": "\t\t[連続スペシャリスト]の概念",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529240591,
      "updated": 1529240751
    },
